gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 114, Spurs 101
gameRecap.excerpt: Alperen Sengun totaled 45 points, 16 rebounds, and 5 steals as the Rockets defeated the Spurs, 114-101, after outscoring them 67-48 in the 2nd half. Jalen Green (23 points) and Fred VanVleet (21 points, 10 assists, five 3PM) totaled 44 points. Devin Vassell (22 points, eight rebounds) and Malaki Branham 20 points) led the Spurs as Victor Wembanyama totaled 10 points, 11 rebounds, and seven blocks. The Rockets move to 27-34 as the Spurs fall to 13-49.
